everyMarket is an e-commerce site with following features.

1. Users can register as sellers and users.
2. sellers can add products to the database and edit and remove the products that they have added.
3. sellers/users can view all products and add products to cart and check out.

Technologies used:
1. Nodejs
2. mongodb
3. Express

Templating engine : ejs.

To run the app first run npm install to install all dependencies.
The app runs on local host port 3000.

Register as seller and add products to start using the app.
